        "cooked": "<p>Actually near Chambolle, but not in the commune of Chambolle: in Gilly-l\u00e8s-C\u00eeteaux! Quite a few Chambolle producers have their regional appellation holdings in that area, such as Roumier and Barthod.</p>",
